('silverwolf_traces', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Generate\")\"><p>Generate</p><p> Bug\"s duration is extended for 1 turn(s). Every time an enemy is inflicted with Weakness Break, Silver Wolf has a 65% base chance of implanting a random Bug in the enemy.</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Inject\")\"><p>Inject</p><p> The duration of the Weakness implanted by Silver Wolf\"s Skill increases by 1 turn(s).</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Side Note\")\"><p>Side Note</p><p> If the enemy has 3 or more debuff(s) when Skill is used, the enemy\"s DMG RES decreases by an extra 5%.</p></button>', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.08)\"><p>ATK Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"Effect Hit Rate\", 0.04)\"><p>Effect Hit Rate Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"Effect Hit Rate\", 0.06)\"><p>Effect Hit Rate Boost 6%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.06)\"><p>ATK Boost 6%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"Quantum\", 0.048)\"><p>DMG Boost: Quantum 5%</p></button>'),
('sushang_traces', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Guileless\")\"><p>Guileless</p><p> When current HP percentage is 50% or lower, reduces the chance of being attacked by enemies.</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Riposte\")\"><p>Riposte</p><p> For every Sword Stance triggered, the DMG dealt by Sword Stance increases by 2%. Stacks up to 10 time(s).</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Vanquisher\")\"><p>Vanquisher</p><p> After using Basic ATK or Skill, if there are enemies on the field with Weakness Break, Sushang\"s action is Advanced Forward by 15%.</p></button>', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"HP\", 0.04)\"><p>HP Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"HP\", 0.06)\"><p>HP Boost 6%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.06)\"><p>ATK Boost 6%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"HP\", 0.08)\"><p>HP Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.08)\"><p>ATK Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"DEF\", 0.075)\"><p>DEF Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"DEF\", 0.05)\"><p>DEF Boost 5%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.06)\"><p>ATK Boost 6%</p></button>'),
('tingyun_traces', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Nourished Joviality\")\"><p>Nourished Joviality</p><p> Tingyun\"s SPD increases by 20% for 1 turn after using Skill.</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Jubilant Passage\")\"><p>Jubilant Passage</p><p> Tingyun immediately regenerates 5 Energy at the start of her turn.</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMajorTraces(\"Knell Subdual\")\"><p>Knell Subdual</p><p> Increases Basic ATK DMG by 40%.</p></button>', '<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"DEF\", 0.05)\"><p>DEF Boost 5%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"DEF\", 0.1)\"><p>DEF Boost 10%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.08)\"><p>ATK Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"Lightning\", 0.048)\"><p>DMG Boost: Lightning 5%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"Lightning\", 0.032)\"><p>DMG Boost: Lightning 3%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.04)\"><p>ATK Boost 4%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"DEF\", 0.075)\"><p>DEF Boost 8%</p></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn\" onclick=\"addMinorTraces(\"ATK\", 0.06)\"><p>ATK Boost 6%</p></button>'),
